SubjectRegulations Establishing Conditions for Making Regulations under Subsection 36(5.2) of the Fisheries Act
PrecisREGULATIONS ESTABLISHING CONDITIONS FOR MAKING REGULATIONS UNDER SUBSECTION 36(5.2) OF THE FISHERIES ACT in order to set out conditions under which each Minister may make regulations authorizing the deposit of deleterious substances into water frequented by fish under their respective responsibilities.
